7503785161-jpeg','','','2015-11-10 21:16:05','2015-11-10 21:16:05','',0,'http://ke5zwg.webhop.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/cropped-received_102038167503785161.jpeg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(40,1,'2015-11-10 21:17:46','2015-11-10 21:17:46','<div style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img src=\"http://ke5zwg.webhop.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/mexico-mtc-sign-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"266\" /></div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"></div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em; text-align: left;\">Elder Finlayson entered the Mexico CCM on Wednesday, October 14, 2015.  What a wonderfully emotional day for all of us!  He will be in Mexico City until November 23 and would love to hear from friends and family.  His address is here on the blog along with an email address.</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em; text-align: left;\">We don\'t know much but that he arrived, said that he was safe and asked for us to write letters.</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em; text-align: left;\">We are grateful that he is willing to serve the Lord and the people of Mexico.  Your prayers on his behalf in learning the language would be great.  There is great power in prayer.</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em; text-align: left;\">His Prep Day will be on Thursday while in the CCM so we will send updates as we get them.</div>\r\n<div style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\" href=\"http://ke5zwg.webhop.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/dsc_0013.jpg\"><img src=\"http://ke5zwg.webhop.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/dsc_0013-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" h