 know where to find the scripture people are looking for! Oh, another great thing, I got a new watch it was only $5!\r\n\r\nMom I have to tell you a story because I love them. So we were saying good bye to the other district and one of the Hermana’s I know was having a hard time with the language and she came over shook my hand and gave me her transfer book. I kept it for a day and a half, I found and wrote 23 scriptures and wrote them for her. She looked at them and broke down crying because she knew it was such a blessing in her life it was amazing to be a tool in her life.  I look forward to being that each day in the field.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_79\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"300\"]<img class=\"wp-image-79 size-medium\" src=\"http://www.elderfinlayson.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/SAM_0151-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"SAM_0151\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /> Celebrating before we leave[/caption]\r\n\r\nParent Note: We received a quick e-mail from Elder Finlayson that he made it to the Mission Presidents home safely on Monday, and would be staying the night. He traveled to his area (a 6 hour bus ride) on Tuesday, but we won\'t hear from him again until next Monday which will be his regular P-Day. Please continue joining us in prayer for his safety as we anxiously await word that he is safely in his area. He said that he is going to one of the few bike missions, and that it is one of the hardest terrains. More like BMX or mountain biking than road bikes.','Preparing to Leave the CCM','','publish','open','open','','preparing-to-leave-the-ccm','','','2015-11-25 18:17:57','2015-11-25 18:17:57','',0,'http://www.elderfinlayson.com/?p=77',0,'post','',0),(78,2,'2015-11-25 18:03:58','2015-11-25 18:03:58','This week we are preparing to head to the field with lots of meetings.  Our Branch President was released which was sad because he is an amazing man who taught us so much.  Another sad thing was that 4 of the missionaries that we know went home this w