its and having fun teaching of the restoration of the gospel of Jesus Christ. I pray that all of you had a wonderful Christmas, and that you will be blessed with all that you require in the new year.  We certainly miss the story-telling in our home. It is truly a miracle that we have this video... On Christmas eve, I was reviewing a site that shared questions to ask your missionary, and came across a link on how to record the call. It mentioned being able to record with google hangout on-air, but we were going to skype. I set-up an on-air hangout so that Kayla and Ethan could join in on talking to our Elder, but when the skype started we was unable to hear us (maybe I\'ll post Jammi\'s frustration with this later). We asked if he could join the hangout and as a result we have a recording of his call, and I was able to pull these clips. We would have been sorely disappointed, but would have made it work, if we had to communicate with him some other way. I know there are some families that were unable to talk to their son\'s or daughters, so I know we were truly blessed.\r\n\r\nEnjoy,\r\nRoger\r\n\r\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=32-IEIdU3IE\r\n\r\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lMb35CKECYk','Christmas Update','','publish','open','open','','christmas-update','','','2015-12-26 15:48:52','2015-12-26 15:48:52','',0,'http://www.elderfinlayson.com/?p=125',0,'post','',0),(126,1,'2015-12-26 15:47:43','2015-12-26 15:47:43','(Dad) - I just want to post a couple of clips from our Christmas call with Elder Finlayson. As you will be able to see, he is in great spirits and having fun teaching of the restoration of the gospel of Jesus Christ. I pray that all of you had a wonderful Christmas, and that you will be blessed with all that you require in the new year.  We certainly miss the story-telling in our home. It is truly a miracle that we have this video... On Christmas eve, I was reviewing a site that shared questions to ask your missionary, and came across a link on how to r