ill and am waiting to get reimbursed.  I am honestly so sad tonight i didn\'t even eat dinner i didn\'t feel like it i do that often now a days. i am going to try to sleep now i don\'t do that very well lol but such is life.\r\n<strong>Martes</strong>\r\ntoday was good ish lol we were in a first lesson and this lady asked us if we wanted to break the law of chastity we were like no thanks! lol My legs are getting so big out here we are up the mountains every day. well i am going to be here for 2 more cambios (changes or transfers) I hope to make senior comp by my 4th or 5th transfer and want to be training by 6 or 7 that\'s my goal and so i am now contacting on my own and i start lessons now and i hold the phone.  i told Hoffman that was my goal and he was like okay here is the phone&lt;\r\n<strong>miercoles</strong>\r\nso today we met Carlos, this man is 84 years old and is strait crazy! He reminds me of papa!\r\nHe knows some English and so in the beginning he was like i am american speak English so i do then he just says stop i am not american we were laughing so hard he was really funny. So today i asked my comp how big is our area he said see those mountains after them there are more and after those ones is the end of our area poop that\'s big lol.  so today we had an amazing lesson with our investigator Eleazar he is so great he has a fecha for the 13 de febrero y he is just the best the only catch is he lives in the rehab center lol (We think that this means that he has a baptism date for the 13th of Feb.  Elder Finlayson said that he needs to come to church a few more times before he can be baptized but they are very hopeful.)\r\n<strong>jeves</strong>\r\ngood day today a lot of grunt work.  walking around contacting people it was good a lot of contacts we finished the week with 20!!!!!! so people here ask all the time if i will come back and visit after the mission and i am like of course i am.   then they ask if i will bring the family and idk i don\'t think so just because well it would be hard lol like i would want to visit cipriano and judy but i couldn\'t bring the family well and y\'all don\'t know Spanish and take my word for it that\'s a hard part lol (Guess we will need to get to work on Spanish so we can go with him to visit his areas!)\r\n<strong>viernes</strong>\r\ngood day i am writing a day late i fell asleep last night no dinner again 3 times this week i am just so tired and not sleeping well, the under side of my eyes are turning purple i just don\'t want the Rojas\' to notice lol they will make a big deal about it lol\r\n<strong>sabado</strong>\r\nbad day!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! my bike broke and i had to get a new part makes me mad and the only time people receive us is so the girls can piñar ( flirt its mission slang ) it makes me so mad like i am not interested, listen to my message it will help you but i don\'t want to flirt that\'s not what i am here for!\r\n<div> <a href=\"http://www.elderfinlayson.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/pn_more_broken_bike_250.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-153\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-153 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.elderfinlayson.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/pn_more_broken_bike_250.jpg\" alt=\"pn_more_broken_bike_250\" width=\"444\" height=\"250\" /></a></div>\r\n<strong>domingo</strong>\r\nHE CAME TH CHURCH i have my first progressing investigator !!!!!!!!! no way i am pumped you have no idea this is crazy.','Week 14-The work is getting \"better\"','','publish','open','open','','week-14-the-work-is-getting-better','','','2016-01-19 16:29:35','2016-01-19 16:29:35','',0,'http://www.elderfinlayson.com/?p=151',0,'post','',0),(152,2,'2016-01-19 16:16:36','2016-01-19 16:16:36','<div>Lunes</div>\r\n<div>good day today really we bought a lot of food and right now i am using my card because i had to pay the electric bill and  am waiting to get reimbursed.  I am honestly so sad tonight i didn\'t even eat dinner i didn